Class WinDivertAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jna.Structure
      • com.github.ffalcinelli.jdivert.windivert.WinDivertAddress

  • public class WinDivertAddress
extends com.sun.jna.Structure
    Represents the "address" of a captured or injected packet. The address includes the packet's headers interfaces and the packet direction. Created by fabio on 20/10/2016.
